# Phase 8 — exclude build-time artifacts and docs from the upload zip.
# Runtime-required files (algo_strategy.py, algo.json, run.sh, gamelib/,
# planner/, offense/, opponent/, archive/, defenses/,
# data/citadel_config_snapshot.json, data/map_elites_archive.json,
# data/opponent_features.npz, opponent/labels.json) are NOT listed here.

# Phase / build documentation at top level
*/STATUS.md
*/AUTONOMOUS_LOG.md
*/FINAL_REPORT.md
*/READY_FOR_UPLOAD.md
*/README.md
*.ps1

# The output zip itself
*/athena_v3.zip

# Tests, eval, sim — never executed at runtime
*/tests/*
*/eval/*
*/sim/*

# All Phase ledger markdown — broad pattern
*/data/PHASE*
*/data/G11_*
*/data/PERF_*
*/data/CONFIG_*
*/data/replay_index.json

# Git / OS noise
*/.git/*
*/.DS_Store
*/__pycache__/*
*.pyc
